             was indicted for <rs id="t18300114-15-off88" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300114-15-off88" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300114-15-off88" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300114-15-victim239" type="victimName">
                           William Butler 
                           Pain
                        <interp inst="t18300114-15-victim239" type="surname" value="Pain"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18300114-15-victim239" type="given" value="William Butler"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18300114-15-victim239" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , on the <rs id="t18300114-15-cd89" type="crimeDate">18th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-15-off88 t18300114-15-cd89"></join>, at St. Paul, Shadwell, and stealing therein, 2 table-cloths, value 3s.; 1 pair of trousers, value 3s., and 1 towel, value 3d., his property; and 1 shawl, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18300114-15-victim240" type="victimName">
                  Ann 
                  Osten
               <interp inst="t18300114-15-victim240" type="surname" value="Osten"></interp>
